column4: There are plenty of fish in the sea, so try this combo instead: Crispy golden shrimp and coleslaw served with Steak Fries® and cocktail sauce.
Crispy chicken tenders and Bottomless Steak Fries® cooked to perfection.
Fried chicken tenders and crispy shrimp docked alongside coleslaw and Steak Fries®. Try it with ranch and cocktail sauce for dipping.
Two fire-grilled chicken breasts basted with authentic Mexican seasonings, topped with fresh salsa and creamy salsa-ranch. Served with a side salad.

Tender sliced prime rib on a cheesy baguette with caramelized onions, horseradish sauce, Provolone and au jus (which is just a fancy word for delicious) for dipping. Served with coleslaw and Steak Fries®.

Premium hand-battered cod fillets, fried to crispy perfection, with our Bottomless Steak Fries®. Served with dill’d and pickle’d tartar sauce. Round out this British
favorite with a pint of ale, old chap!
Our classic clucks tossed in Buzz sauce and served with fries.
A perfectly pan-seared 6-oz. salmon fillet served with bottomless steamed broccoli and house-made coleslaw.
Premium Hand Battered cod fillets and golden shrimp served with coleslaw and bottomless steak fries plus cocktail sauce and dill'd and pickle'd tarter sauce for dipping.
